Mage- (6)
- May choose to use one of three abilities:
- Abilities:
  1. Conjure Barrier - Give one Weak Protection to a player for the night. [4 phase cooldown]
  2. Arcane Vision - Find out someone's exact role (but not colour faction). [6 phase cooldown]
  3. Magic Burst - Kills themself in order to cast a Strong Attack on another player. (Unblockable attack on self. Both attacks are end phase)
- Respawns in 6 phases.
